summary: Completed comprehensive frontend testing of Next.js App Router application. All core features tested successfully including navigation, authentication redirects, form functionality, and page rendering. One minor issue identified with pricing CTA redirect behavior.
passed_tests: Home page loads with hero/CTAs and logo - all elements render correctly
Navigation links route to Pricing/Apply/Login - all nav links functional
Pricing page monthly/annual toggle works correctly
Pricing page displays authentication alert for unauthenticated users
Pricing CTA redirects unauthenticated users to /login with next parameter
Apply page renders all form fields and submit button correctly
Apply form fields accept input and validation works
Login page renders sign-in form and toggle to create account
Login page toggle between sign-in and create account modes works
Dashboard route redirects to /login when not authenticated with next parameter
Billing success page renders with correct content and buttons
Billing cancel page renders with correct content and buttons
Privacy page renders with all sections and correct content
Terms page renders with all sections and correct content
